OL,6,FAttorney General Victoria Prentis
OL,7,Fsaid: "Valdo Calocane's crimes were
OL,8,Fhorrific and have shocked a nation. He
OL,9,Fbrutally killed three innocent people
OL,10,Fand violently attacked three other
OL,11,Fvictims.
OL,13,F"Their experiences will stay in our
OL,14,Fminds for a long time to come."
