OL,6,FShe continued: "This was a case that
OL,7,Fevoked strong feelings amongst so many
OL,8,Fpeople and it was no surprise that I
OL,9,Freceived so many referrals under the
OL,10,Funduly lenient sentence scheme to
OL,11,Fconsider the hospital order handed to
OL,12,FCalocane.
OL,14,F"My duty as a law officer in
OL,15,Fconsidering whether sentences may be
OL,16,Funduly lenient is to act independently
OL,17,Fof government, even when it is not
OL,18,Feasy or popular.
